:"真白","body":"真的耶。\n感覺很適合小透","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"area4705-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"啊，小白真的很有眼光耶～！\n對了！　人家就來挑個適合小白的單品吧！\n二之助，一起來找吧！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"area4705-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windowDisplayName":"筑紫","body":"可以是可以，但瑠唯同學他們不是馬上就要回來了嗎？\n他們也有說只是去拿個東西而已","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":29,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":29,"voiceId":"area4705-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"久等了～。\n我們成功拿完東西囉～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"area4705-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"這只是學生會的事，\n我認為你們沒有跟過來的必要","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"area4705-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windowDisplayName":"筑紫","body":"真是的！　別說這麼見外的話！\n我們已經決定只要瑠唯同學有困擾就會出手幫忙了！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":29,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":29,"voiceId":"area4705-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"我其實也根本沒有感到困擾……算了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"serious02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"area4705-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"所以勒！？\n瑠唯去拿了什麼東西？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"area4705-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"啊哈哈哈……原來透透不知道啊","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"area4705-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"真白","body":"我記得好像有說過是，小學部要辦的聖誕節活動的裝飾？\n說是活動要用，但數量好像有點少……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"area4705-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"這是拿來補充那些太舊或壞掉用的份。\n準備活動用的全部用品，並不是我們的工作","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"area4705-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windowDisplayName":"筑紫","body":"這些會拿來裝飾小學部中庭那棵很大的樹喔！\n那個真的很漂亮，很值得期待喔！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":29,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":29,"voiceId":"area4705-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"真白","body":"嗯，因為我是第一次看，所以還蠻期待的……\n而且月森的聖誕活動也應該蠻豪華的吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"kandou01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"area4705-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"嗯嗯。\n完全不會輸給這個購物中心的裝飾喔～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"area4705-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"啊，這裡一整片都已經聖誕氣氛到不行了，\n人家居然還沒拍照！\n要趕快拍一張傳給紗夜學姊他們看！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"area4705-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"真白","body":"小透，很快就和學姊變熟了，真的好厲害喔……\n哪像我，只是要傳給香澄學姊一則訊息，\n就煩惱了兩天","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"area4705-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windowDisplayName":"筑紫","body":"那，那也煩惱太久了吧……\n不過，也真的會想和其他學姊們變更要好沒錯！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":29,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":29,"voic